item.title: CVE-2017-1129|2024-09-16T16:38:43.778Z -- ibm -- lotus%20expeditor
item.description: IBM Notes 8.5 and 9.0 is vulnerable to a denial of service. If a user is persuaded to click on a malicious link, it could cause the Notes client to hang and have to be restarted. IBM X-Force ID: 121370.
